WEBVTT

00:07:29.855 --> 00:07:33.418
If we connect the world
as fast as the heck we can,

00:07:33.442 --> 00:07:35.367
yes, we'll make money from this stuff,

00:07:35.391 --> 00:07:37.358
but it's going to be fundamentally good."

00:07:37.382 --> 00:07:38.906
It just wasn't foreseen --

00:07:38.930 --> 00:07:41.261
RM: They got to 1.7 billion monthly users

00:07:41.285 --> 00:07:44.370
before anything really bad
showed up on the platform.

00:07:45.577 --> 00:07:48.886
Listen, I say this as somebody
who is currently a critic,

00:07:48.910 --> 00:07:50.934
but you still have to admire

00:07:50.958 --> 00:07:54.224
how extraordinary the accomplishment was
to get to 1.7 billion

00:07:54.248 --> 00:07:55.569
before anything went wrong.

00:07:55.593 --> 00:07:58.918
The problem was
once you passed that threshold,

00:07:58.942 --> 00:08:01.116
all of a sudden,